channel.title: I'm glad we're a joke to you
channel.description:
This would make the [b]SECOND[/b] time [b]THIS MONTH[/b] I've had trouble with your goddamn server status. If you haven't noticed, your stupid fucking PHP scripts [b]DO NOT[/b] work, & it's displaying only one server, although you recieved $3,000+ this month for all 10 servers.
I've sent a claim into paypal, along with sabsabi. Hope to hear from you.
Much Love, Project 72
